USAGE OF THE PROJECT

1 -INSTALL ESPTOOL
	https://www.flamingo-tech.nl/2021/03/21/installing-and-using-esptools/

2 - INSTALL MICROPYTHON Firmware
	https://docs.sunfounder.com/projects/esp32-starter-kit/en/latest/micropython/python_start/install_micropython.html

3 - DOCKER CONTAINER IMAGE FOR SERVERAPP:
	docker pull mardoche/audiokyria:latest

4 - DOCKER CONTAINER IMAGE FOR WEBAPP :
	docker pull mardoche/webwav:tagname

5- RUN IMAGE SERVERAPP: 
	docker run -d --name webwav -v path/to/shared_folder:/app/shared -p 5000:5000 webwav
	docker run -d --name audiokyria -v path/to/shared_folder:/app/shared -p 40500:40500 audiokyria

